reviews.text: If you like spicy Chinese foods.(Sichuan style), this is one of the places on Hong Kong Island that I will go. Clean and good quality of food. They also have a good selections of non-spicy dishes. I also like the red bean sweet soup they serve for free when you finish the meal.
Great value, great taste, great decor, and  portions big. Recommend !

Very classic and exciting Sichuan cuisine, not just one taste, everything spicy with a character! Great service, friendly staff that offer good recommendations. Not far from MTR station, very easy to a access.👍
Really great food and wonderful service. Will be back again

Really liked the food in this restaurant in Wan Chai. Braised beef with eggplants was very tasty. The pan-fried dumplings as well. They have a lot of choice when it comes to shishuan food. Portions were pretty big too.

result.name: 天府人家

reviews.text: 食物好味, 但價錢較貴

If you like spicy Chinese foods.(Sichuan style), this is one of the places on Hong Kong Island that I will go. Clean and good quality of food. They also have a good selections of non-spicy dishes. I also like the red bean sweet soup they serve for free when you finish the meal.
파왕샹로우 정말맛있었다. 볶음밥에 해산물도 적당히 들어있었고 후식으로 단팥물?과 시원한 향의 곤약 젤리같은게 나온다. 음식 맛있음
環境比較噪，食物都普通，如果呢個價錢，係灣仔就有十分多可以選擇，麻麻啦

접시가 깨끗하지 않아서 직접 접시보관하는 캐비넷을 열어서 골라 사용했고, 처음에 하얀국물이랑 빨간국물 담아오는 냄비에 수세미 조각 끼여있어서 헐...했는데 뭐 완차이 지역이 다 그렇지...싶어서 그냥 바꿔가져와달라고 서버에게 요청했습니다. 그리고 빨간국물이 두입 이상 계속 먹기 힘들정도로 맵습니다. 처음엔 번갈아 먹어도 나중엔 하얀국물만 먹고 나왔네요. 맵기가 마라탕보다 더 매워요. 소고기, 통조림햄(스팸), 동그란 어묵, 생선껍질튀김, 쑥갓, 팽이버섯+느타리버섯, 언두부, 두유로 만든 얇은 두부피, 면 이렇게 주문해먹었는데 세사람이서 배가 터지게 먹고 나왔습니다^-^ 다음에 또 가고 싶어요. 서버들은 모두 상냥하고 친절했습니다.
